Title: Rogue Agent
Description:
We lost Y'tekhi.

We can worry about the how of it later. Right now, we need to worry about taking them down before they make things worse.

<Lilian snorts.>

I guess we came down here to find out what Xal'atath had up her sleeve. ...I wish we'd minded our own business.
CompletionText: Hard to think of how this could have gone any worse.
RewardText:
We're out of the public eye, for a moment.

Getting Y'tekhi back to the Weaver is my priority. Yours is dealing with the weapons.
